{"lemma":"سَقْيٌ","slug":"سَقْيٌ","root":"س.ق.#","root_slug":"س-ق-_","root_link":"/words/roots/س-ق-_","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"سَقْيٌ","root":"سقي","pos":"V","occurrence_count":12},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["verb"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["","n20140","n20141","n20145"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B3%D9%8E%D9%82%D9%92%D9%8A%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to give (someone) (a drink)","tags":["ditransitive"],"examples":[{"text":"وَسَقَاهُمْ رَبُّهُمْ شَرَابًا طَهُورًا","english":"and their Lord will give them a purifying drink."}]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to give water to, to quench the thirst of, to hydrate","tags":["transitive"]},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to water","tags":["transitive"],"examples":[{"text":"وَفِي ٱلْأَرْضِ قِطَعٌ مُتَجَاوِرَاتٌ وَجَنَّاتٌ مِنْ أَعْنَابٍ وَزَرْعٌ وَنَخِيلٌ صِنْوَانٌ وَغَيْرُ صِنْوَانٍ يُسْقَى بِمَاءٍ وَاحِدٍ وَنُفَضِّلُ بَعْضَهَا عَلَىٰ بَعْضٍ فِي ٱلْأُكُلِ إِنَّ فِي ذَٰلِكَ لَآيَاتٍ لِقَوْمٍ يَعْقِلُونَ","english":"And within the land are neighboring plots and gardens of grapevines and crops and palm trees, [growing] several from a root or otherwise, watered with one water; and We favor and privilege some of them over the others in eating. Indeed, in that are signs for thinking men."}]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From the root س ق ي (s q y). Cognate with Hebrew הִשְׁקָה (hishká)."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n20140","headword_ar":"سَقْى","root":"sqY","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"in the phrase"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saqoYu AlfuraAti","text_ar":"سَقْىُ الفُرَاتِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The towns,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"villages,"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lands,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"watered by the Euphrates,"},{"kind":"text","text":"is said by Mtr to be an inf. n. used as a subst. [properly so termed, and, being originally an inf. n., it may be used alike as sing. and pl.]; or, in this phrase, a noun that should be prefixed to it [such as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*aAt","text_ar":"ذَات"},{"kind":"text","text":"], is suppressed: or, accord. to some, it is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"siqoY","text_ar":"سِقْى"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.], an instance of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiEolN","text_ar":"فِعْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the sense of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mafoEuwlN","text_ar":"مَفْعُولٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and thus it is in the handwriting of EI- Hareeree in his 22nd Makámeh. (Har p. 246.) ―         -b2-  See also the next paragraph."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n20141","headword_ar":"سِقْىٌ","root":"sqY","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Drink;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what is drunk;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what is given to drink;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA;) a subst. from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saqaAhu","text_ar":"سَقَاهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asoqaAhu","text_ar":"اَسْقَاهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (S, TA; [in the former of which, this meaning is indicated, and also the meaning of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"water given to drink to cattle;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"water with which land is irrigated;"},{"kind":"text","text":"]) in the M,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"drink given to camels:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asoqiyapN","text_ar":"اَسْقِيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, TA.) And [particularly]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A share,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"portion, of water"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for irrigation"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kamo siqoYu A^aroDika","text_ar":"كَمْ سِقْىُ اَرْضِكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"How many bucketfuls"},{"kind":"text","text":"or skinfuls, (the specificative being suppressed,) virtually meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"how much, is the share,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"portion, of water for the irrigation of thy land?"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, TA.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Water,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA, [in the CK"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mA","text_ar":"ما"},{"kind":"text","text":", a mistranscription for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA='N","text_ar":"مَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",]) i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"yellow water"},{"kind":"text","text":"[meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"serum,"},{"kind":"text","text":"effused in dropsy],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"incidental in the belly,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,) scarcely, or never, curable; (TA;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saqoYN","text_ar":"سَقْىٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K: ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wayufotaHu","text_ar":"وَيُفْتَحُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"being there added: and the word as meaning “ yellow water ” is written only with fet-h in the JK: but in the TA,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wyftH","text_ar":"ويفتح"},{"kind":"text","text":"forms part of the addition here following:]) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it is in white"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nafaAfiyx","text_ar":"نَفَافِيخ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cells"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in the fat of the belly;"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in which sense, also, the word is written only with fet-h in the JK;]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and it"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. meaning the belly]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"is opened"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wayufotaHu","text_ar":"وَيُفْتَحُ"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"on the occasion of its issuing:"},{"kind":"text","text":"so says ISd: (TA:) a subst. from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saqaY baTonuhu","text_ar":"سَقَى بَطْنُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.]. (S, TA.) And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A skin"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"membrane"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"containing yellow water, which cleaves asunder from over the head of the young one"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"at the birth"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (K, TA:) or, as in the T, the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"water that is in the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"membrane called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ma$iymap","text_ar":"مَشِيمَة"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that comes forth"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaY raA^osi Alwaladi","text_ar":"عَلَى رَاْسِ الوَلَدِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[meaning at the birth]. (TA.)       -A2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Land that is irrigated;"},{"kind":"text","text":"having the meaning of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mafoEuwlN","text_ar":"مَفْعُولٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"niqoDN","text_ar":"نِقْضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in the sense of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"manoquwDN","text_ar":"مَنْقُوضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (Er-Rághib, TA: [see also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saqoY","text_ar":"سَقْى"},{"kind":"text","text":":]) or it signifies, (K,) or so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saqiY~N","text_ar":"سَقِىٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", of the same measure as"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aqiY~N","text_ar":"شَقِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"SabiY~N","text_ar":"صَبِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Mgh,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"masoqawiY~N","text_ar":"مَسْقَوِىٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Mgh, K,) app. a rel. n. from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"masoqFY","text_ar":"مَسْقًى"},{"kind":"text","text":", not from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"masoqiY~N","text_ar":"مَسْقِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", for if it were from the latter it would be"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"masoqiY~N","text_ar":"مَسْقِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, TA,) [or, accord. to some, if from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"masoqiY~N","text_ar":"مَسْقِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", it may be either"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"masoqiY~N","text_ar":"مَسْقِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"masoqawiY~N","text_ar":"مَسْقَوِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (see Lumsden's Arab. Gr. p. 630,)] seed-produce"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"irrigated"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by water running upon the surface of the earth;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Mgh;) [i. e., not by rain only;] ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saqiY~N","text_ar":"سَقِىٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"being the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baxosiY~N","text_ar":"بَخْسِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (Mgh;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"masoqawiY~N","text_ar":"مَسْقَوِىٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"contr. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maZomay^iY~N","text_ar":"مَظْمَيِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Mgh, TA,) which signifies “ watered [only] by the rain; ” and the vulgar say ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"misoqaAwiY","text_ar":"مِسْقَاوِى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["TA","K","Mgh","S","M"]},{"entry_id":"n20145","headword_ar":"سَقِىٌّ","root":"sqY","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"siqoYN","text_ar":"سِقْىٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", last sentence, in two places. ―         -b2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A cloud having large drops"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of rain"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (S, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vehement in the falling"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thereof"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S:) [like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ramiY~N","text_ar":"رَمِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rawiY~N","text_ar":"رَوِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":":] pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asoqiyapN","text_ar":"اَسْقِيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, K.) ―         -b3-  And The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"papyrus"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"barodiY~","text_ar":"بَرْدِىّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"): (JK, S, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tender papyrus:"},{"kind":"text","text":"so called because of its growing in, or near to, water: (TA:) occurring in a verse of Imra-el- Keys, cited voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mu*al~alN","text_ar":"مُذَلَّلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, TA: [but see what is said under this word,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"m*l~l","text_ar":"مذلّل"},{"kind":"text","text":": and see Ham p. 555:]) n. un."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saqiy~apN","text_ar":"سَقِيَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S.) ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Palm-trees;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saqiy~apN","text_ar":"سَقِيَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies [the same, or]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"palmtrees that are irrigated by means of water-wheels"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dawaAlK","text_ar":"دَوَالٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", [pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daAliyapN","text_ar":"دَالِيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", q. v.]). (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","JK","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}